title: Greater Cleveland Film Commission to host exclusive screening of 'Star Wars: The Force Awakens'
text:
Published By: Cleveland.com: Movies - Today 
The organization will host an exclusive, first public screening of "Star Wars: The Force Awakens" on Thursday, Dec. 17 at 7 p.m....
